  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017560836-FFHKFP00ITENMCTZZJQ4/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Once again I've partnered with <a href=\"http://www.CreativeOptionsCrafts.com\">Creative Options®</a> to help me get organized! Yes, it is a work in progress always, but I have to say I have gotten a lot better at (mostly) putting things back where they belong. My biggest challenge seems to be more the accumulation and piling up of the stuff more than anything else. <a href=\"http://www.CreativeOptionsCrafts.com\">Creative Options®</a> has fashionable and functional storage solutions perfect for crafts of all kinds and gift giving. I even used one of the totes to show how it can be a travel treasure chest for Jack! Here are the new totes they sent over. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6b-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017592283-0U4EKVNC5OXCYU1GMYPU/6b-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6c-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017591476-LNZYFZIAGRTKIOY536A5/6c-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6d-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017631086-7FCV5XEM8GYSAWPNSZA0/6d-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6e-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017630836-HJH6S70G876YVONUYOUE/6e-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6f-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017595460-0P7J6C9PKQ8Y08922IF1/6f-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The Total Tote in Vineyard is so versatile and functional. It features hybrid construction, which combines the look of a soft-sided organizer with the rigid body of a Creative Options molded product. The result is clever storage that keeps its shape. It's \"tote-ally\" awesome and available in-stores at Joann Fabric and Crafts.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6g-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017673227-E7EJ17PRNX4NOQ97GFHZ/6g-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6h-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017673902-0HN7JLM6XYX0JNJCI2J3/6h-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I used the Crochet Tote in Viva La Pink print as a planning kit as well as for crocheting. It's available in-stores and <a href=\"http://goo.gl/99RTGM\">online here at Joann Fabrics and Crafts</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6i-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017721845-J3U83W89SYH6ZE7L445R/6i-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6j-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017722646-ZNLX6WB8U3BS68X9DMNP/6j-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6k-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017744416-A53UGGV9HRF1PYHHIE1G/6k-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The Knitting Needle Roll Up in Viva La Pink print is available on <a href=\"http://amzn.to/1O1YnHQ\">Amazon</a> and at <a href=\"http://goo.gl/Xarybf\">Joann</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6l-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017773295-0AGBWHD3P5LPCUPSUJZ1/6l-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6m-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017774366-2579L9VIQW7BJ6CNKJJ7/6m-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The Tapered Tote in \"Viva La Pink\" is sold out online but available at Michaels.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6n-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017833976-8AF4KOSMKH2RX04PK84G/6n-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6o-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017833977-NL2UQ539OMYNWE41WB04/6o-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6p-Amy+Tangerine+++Creative+Options+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1596017835298-P8SPA0ROLVMZ5H9TZKN0/6p-Amy%2BTangerine%2B%2B%2BCreative%2BOptions%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Large Signature 5-Pocket Tote in Andee Cool print is available in-stores at Hobby Lobby and <a href=\"http://goo.gl/LaCpmM\">online at Joann</a> and <a href=\"http://goo.gl/nzu55a\">Walmart</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Here's <a href=\"https://youtu.be/0wXyJ0cXobI\">the video</a> showing all of the totes in action. To find out more about Creative Options® Storage Solutions go to: http://www.CreativeOptionsCrafts.com. For crafting tips, giveaways, and product news, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/creativeoptionscrafts\">'Like' Creative Options® on Facebook</a>.</p><p>You can also see how some creative friends styled their totes in these posts by <a href=\"http://www.one-happy-mama.com/2015/12/creative-options-a-super-cute-organizing-solution.html\">One Happy Mama</a>, <a href=\"http://www.mypurpleylife.com/2015/12/journaling-on-go-with-creative-options.html\">My Purpley Life</a>, and <a href=\"http://allforthememories.com/blog/2015/12/08/organizing-craft-supplies-for-the-unorganized-part-1/\">All For The Memories</a>.</p><p>DISCLAIMER: This post is sponsored by Creative Options. As always, all thoughts and opinions are my own. </p>"
}